<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Home - Buy-Sell-X</title>
  <style>
    /* Basic Reset */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #74ebd5, #ACB6E5, #a18cd1);
      color: #2c3e50;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .container {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      padding: 40px 60px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #fff;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      color: #f1f1f1;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, #3498db, #8e44ad);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 14px 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      display: inline-block;
    }

    a:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, #2980b9, #6c3483);
      transform: scale(1.07);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome to Buy-Sell-X</h1>
    <p>
      Your trusted online marketplace to buy, sell, and discover amazing products.  
      From gadgets and fashion to services and daily essentials â€“ we connect buyers 
      and sellers in one powerful platform. Start exploring now and find exactly what you need!
    </p>
    <a href="/listings"> Explore Website</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
